playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/46b8b89077244dce53a7474510ce8ec1.poster.avif?t=1773942008\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/46b8b89077244dce53a7474510ce8ec1.webm?t=1773942008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/46b8b89077244dce53a7474510ce8ec1.mp4?t=1773942008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Decarnation's Rêve and Cauchemar soundtracks feature contributions from numerous artists, including the renowned composer <strong>Akira Yamaoka</strong> (Silent Hill) whose works blend horror and the paranormal, breathing life into this nightmarish tale.<br><br><i>\"I'm delighted to have been able to take part in the development of Decarnation [...] I've developed a special bond with this game.</i><br><br>Numerous references and inspirations from cult horror works have shaped the world of Decarnation - can you spot them all?",
